data.description: Nestled on Bent Mountain, this charming 1.5-story home sits on 22 acres of natural splendor. It includes a detached 2-car garage shop with a private apartment - ideal for hobbies, guests, or extra income.  This home was pre-inspected by a licensed home inspector. 13 mo. Home Warranty thru Home Warranty of America is offered. Out-of-market agents to book appts M-F 9am-4pm (excluding holidays)
